{#
   context_recall.j2
   Injects relevant past diagnosis history into
   the current session for personalised responses.
   
   Variables:
   - past_diagnoses: list of past diagnosis dicts
   - farmer_name: optional string
#}

{% if past_diagnoses %}
This farmer has the following relevant diagnosis history:

{% for diagnosis in past_diagnoses %}
{{ loop.index }}. Date: {{ diagnosis.date }}
   Plant: {{ diagnosis.plant_identified }}
   Disease: {{ diagnosis.diagnosis_name }}
   Severity: {{ diagnosis.severity }}
   {% if diagnosis.treatment_summary %}
   Treatment: {{ diagnosis.treatment_summary }}
   {% endif %}

{% endfor %}

Use this history to:
- Note if the same disease is recurring
- Observe whether the condition is improving
  or getting worse over time
- Reference previous treatments that may 
  have succeeded or failed
- Provide more personalised advice based on
  this farmer's specific situation

{% else %}
This is the farmer's first diagnosis session.
No previous history is available.
Provide general advice appropriate for a 
first-time user of the application.
{% endif %}